RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: Rcpp, RcppParallel, mgcv, stats, Rdpack
RdMacros: Rdpack
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen, RcppParallel
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: 
  CPU with AVX/SSE4.2 (optional for better performance)
